{"tid":1004581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Brusted]學警未出更先食物中毒！ 黃竹坑警校25人食咖喱飯中招","createTime":"2019-02-01T14:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T02:26:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"941f93e3f998bd63941745f70cb429ec8b0613c6","tid":1004581,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"當香港同支那睇齊用&quot;質量&quot;一詞去取代&quot;品質&quot;，你就知所有o野都會同支那接軌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190201/59213403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190201%2F59213403&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=143b3e75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190201%2F59213403&h=94c21d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190201/59213403</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【更新：新增警方回應】<br />\n位於黃竹坑的警察學院爆出集體食物中毒事件，有25名警員在飯堂用膳後出現腹痛和腹瀉，目前全部患者情況穩定。衞生防護中心發言人稱已就事故通知食物環境衞生署，並正繼續調查。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心公佈，警校內25名年齡介乎19至41歲的男子，於1月29日在校內午膳，各人進食咖喱薯仔炆排骨拼魚腐飯後，約8至23小時內陸續出現腹痛和腹瀉等病徵，當中有兩人曾經求醫，毋須入院。中心呼籲市民應保持個人、食物及環境衞生，預防經由食物傳播的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人回覆稱，該25名警員是在校內食用食用了同一承辦商所提供的午餐後，出現腹痛及腹瀉等病徵。香港警察學院已即時跟進該承辦商的服務，會繼續監察該承辦商所提供的膳食<span style=\"color: red;\">質量</span>水平和安全情況。"},{"pid":"6205f9bda829965a0332609e7fc0cf7a2219d57a","tid":1004581,"uid":121185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"畀狗食洗撚咁高質素咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5fa9f2e9ec1bb2d72bf234dd1a5fc4f15cea3b","tid":1004581,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"食唔慣人飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50948213cae27e0198971351b97124a5ff19d8f","tid":1004581,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"學警（食物中毒）"},{"pid":"457948944b45cd53614a104715d9c91a8fd48532","tid":1004581,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係 brusted <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}